prompt: Summarize the following story in first person: Finally It was happened. we got visa to america. It was a long time dream for my husband and me. My husband and me are Australian couple. We tried to move America for past one and half year. My husband is a software engineer. His childhood dream is to settle in USA. this is also my dream. he working in a software company for 4 years. He is a talented decision maker. So company promoted him as senior manager. after this incident, he try to focus on his dream of america. His company has lot of branches in various countries around the world. he find branch in USA in Internet. Yes. His search gave a good result . His company's branch located in California, Texas and NewYork. He was choose California to work. Then he properly apply for transformation process in company. Company cooperated his activities because , California branch need a good worker at the time. So my husband used this opportunity. He was moving the green card process properly. After long time of process, finally we got an expected mail from USCIS. That mail contains the information that both of us elected to get green card. It is happiest moment in our life. Now we filed for Australian Visa. After few days we ready to make journey to America.
